---
title: Easy Spaghetti and Bacon Ragout with Parm and Hidden Veggies
description: This spaghetti in red sauce is built on the smoky flavour of bacon! Mirepoix, mushrooms, garlic and red pepper pesto all make this sauce a flavour bomb in a short amount of time!

